      "text": "When valve head has been worn down to 0.5 mm (0.020 in) in margin thickness, replace valve.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Grinding allowance for valve stem tip is 0.2 mm (0.008 in) or less.",
